'''936 ABC Hobart''' (call sign: '''7ZR''') is the [[ABC Local Radio]] station for [[Hobart]], [[Tasmania]], owned by the [[Australian Broadcasting Corporation]]. It broadcasts on 936 [[kilohertz|kHz]] on the [[amplitude modulation|AM]] band.
